#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:2
msgid "基本概念"
msgstr "Basic Concepts"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:5
msgid "JVM"
msgstr "JVM"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:6
msgid "JVM是Java平台的核心，以机器代码来实现，为程序执行提供了所需的所有基本功能，例如字节码解析器、JIT编译器、垃圾收集器等。由于它是机器代码实现的，其同样受到二进制文件受到的攻击。"
msgstr "The JVM is the core of the Java platform. It is implemented in machine code and provides all basic functions required for program execution, such as the bytecode interpreter, JIT compiler, and garbage collector. Because it is implemented as machine code, it is also exposed to the same attacks that affect binary files."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:8
msgid "JCL是JVM自带的一个标准库，含有数百个系统类。默认情况下，所有系统类都是可信任的，且拥有所有的特权。"
msgstr "JCL is a standard library bundled with the JVM and contains hundreds of system classes. By default, all system classes are trusted and have all privileges."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:11
msgid "JDK"
msgstr "JDK"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:12
msgid ""
"Java开发工具包(Java Development Kit，JDK)是Oracle公司发布的Java平台，有标准版(Standard "
"Edition，Java SE)、企业版(Enterprise Edition，Java EE)等版本。"
msgstr ""
"The Java Development Kit (JDK) is the Java platform released by Oracle. It "
"includes editions such as Standard Edition (Java SE) and Enterprise Edition "
"(Java EE)."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:14
msgid "在最开始，JDK以二进制形式发布，而后在2006年11月17日，Sun以GPL许可证发布了Java的源代码，于是之后出现了OpenJDK。"
msgstr "Initially, the JDK was released in binary form. Later, on November 17, 2006, Sun released the Java source code under the GPL license, which led to OpenJDK."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:17
msgid "JMX"
msgstr "JMX"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:18
msgid ""
"JMX(Java Management "
"Extensions，Java管理扩展)是一个为应用程序植入管理功能的框架，主要为管理和监视应用程序、系统对象、设备和面向服务的网络提供相应的工具。JMX可以远程读取系统中的值、调用系统中的方法。在JMX未配置身份验证或JDK版本过低存在反序列化漏洞时，可能会导致远程代码执行。"
msgstr ""
"JMX (Java Management Extensions) is a framework for embedding management "
"capabilities into applications. It mainly provides tools for managing and "
"monitoring applications, system objects, devices, and service-oriented "
"networks. JMX can remotely read values from a system and invoke methods in "
"the system. If JMX is not configured with authentication, or if the JDK "
"version is too old and has a deserialization vulnerability, remote code "
"execution may result."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:21
msgid "JNI"
msgstr "JNI"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:22
msgid "JNI (Java Native Interface) 是Java提供的和其他语言交互的接口。"
msgstr "JNI (Java Native Interface) is the interface provided by Java for interacting with other languages."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:25
msgid "JNA"
msgstr "JNA"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:26
msgid ""
"JNA (Java Native Access) 是在JNI上的框架，用于自动实现Java接口到native "
"function的映射，而不需要另外编写JNI代码。"
msgstr ""
"JNA (Java Native Access) is a framework built on JNI that automatically maps "
"Java interfaces to native functions without requiring additional JNI code."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:29
msgid "OGNL"
msgstr "OGNL"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:30
msgid ""
"OGNL(Object-Graph Navigation "
"Language，对象导航语言)是一种功能强大的表达式语言，通过简单一致的表达式语法，提供了存取对象的任意属性、调用对象的方法、遍历整个对象的结构图、实现字段类型转化等功能。"
msgstr ""
"OGNL (Object-Graph Navigation Language) is a powerful expression language. "
"Through a simple and consistent expression syntax, it provides capabilities "
"such as accessing arbitrary object properties, invoking object methods, "
"traversing an entire object graph, and performing field type conversion."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:32
msgid "Struts2中使用了OGNL，提供了一个ValueStack类。ValueStack分为root和context两部分。root中是当前的action对象，context中是ActionContext里面所有的内容。"
msgstr "Struts2 uses OGNL and provides a ValueStack class. ValueStack is divided into root and context. The root contains the current action object, and the context contains all content in ActionContext."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:35
msgid "IO模型"
msgstr "I/O Model"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:36
msgid "Java 对操作系统的各种 IO 模型进行了封装，形成了不同的API。"
msgstr "Java encapsulates various operating system I/O models and exposes them through different APIs."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:39
msgid "BIO"
msgstr "BIO"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:40
msgid "BIO (Blocking I/O) 是同步阻塞I/O模式，数据的读取写入必须阻塞在一个线程内等待其完成。"
msgstr "BIO (Blocking I/O) is a synchronous blocking I/O model. Data reads and writes must block within a thread until they complete."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:43
msgid "NIO"
msgstr "NIO"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:44
msgid ""
"NIO (New I/O) 是一种同步非阻塞的I/O模型，在Java 1.4中引入，对应 java.nio 包，提供了 Channel , "
"Selector，Buffer等抽象。"
msgstr ""
"NIO (New I/O) is a synchronous non-blocking I/O model introduced in Java "
"1.4. It corresponds to the java.nio package and provides abstractions such "
"as Channel, Selector, and Buffer."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:47
msgid "AIO"
msgstr "AIO"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:48
msgid "AIO (Asynchronous I/O) 在 Java 7 中引入，是NIO的改进版，是异步非阻塞的IO模型，基于事件和回调机制实现。"
msgstr "AIO (Asynchronous I/O) was introduced in Java 7. It is an improved version of NIO and is an asynchronous non-blocking I/O model implemented through events and callbacks."

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:51
msgid "反射"
msgstr "Reflection"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:54
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/language/java/basic.rst:55
msgid "Java反射机制是指在运行状态中，对于任意一个类，都能够知道这个类的所有属性和方法；对于任意一个对象，都能够调用它的任意方法和属性；这种动态获取信息以及动态调用对象方法的功能被称为语言的反射机制。"
msgstr "Java reflection refers to the ability, at runtime, to inspect all properties and methods of any class and to invoke any method or access any property of any object. This ability to dynamically obtain information and dynamically call object methods is called the language's reflection mechanism."

